      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="41485987">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/92585859/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u92585859-1.jpg" alt="你的美好结局" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/41485987/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/41485987/" class="">如何当一个好皇帝——汉朝兴亡</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/92585859/" class=" " title="你的美好结局">你的美好结局</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="41485987">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">文景之治
武帝中兴
王莽代汉
刘秀建立东汉王朝
东汉衰败</span>
